N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 263.44 - Answer; failure to file

State Regulations

If the party or parties against whom the charge is
brought fails to file a timely answer as required, the hearing officer may deem
such failure to constitute an admission of the material facts alleged in the
charge. Notes
